          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Modernizing Credit Opportunities Act</b></p> <p>This bill provides that&nbsp;an agreement between&nbsp;an insured depository institution and a third-party service provider shall not affect (1) the&nbsp;depository institution's role as&nbsp;lender, or (2) the determination of the location of the depository institution.</p>]]></text>
